TXT_HEROS_INFO: Hero Unit Info Display
TXT_HEROS_INFO_DESC: Show independent icons for hero units on the top-right corner; click to select unit (or its transport if inside); if already selected, centers view; shows health, shield and Iron Curtain timer (or production progress if being built); when under Iron Curtain, a semi-transparent black overlay appears; low health shows a reddish tint; when under attack, flashes red; when attacking, flashes yellow; when under airstrike designator, flashes red; when under chrono lock, flashes blue; when under Magnetron or Disruptor, flashes purple; when EMP'd, flashes gray; when inside transport or bunker, shows blue border around health bar; when inside transport, health, shield and Iron Curtain timer show those of the transport.
TXT_HEROS_VISIBLE: Hero Unit Info: On
TXT_HEROS_INVISIBLE: Hero Unit Info: Off
