LoadBrief:Confederation: Atlas Confederation (AC) focuses on nuclear technology, excels at harassment and raids; its radiation is deadly to vehicles and infantry.
LoadBrief:Russians: Soviet Russia (RU) has a unique dual-tech tree (choose one). Build [Magnetic Assembly Plant] for electromagnetic tech to use EMP, or [Battlefield Intelligence Bureau] for industrial tech focused on frontal assault.
LoadBrief:China: Eastern United Front (EUF) possesses the world's most advanced missile systems, uses Iron Curtain and missile defense, and has superweapons for long-range strikes. It has strong frontline resilience and attrition capability.
LoadBrief:Europa: Europa Joint Council (EJC) is defense-oriented, excels at ambushes and defensive positions, with reliable heavy armor and strong fortifications.
LoadBrief:Americans: United States of America (USA) is known for powerful air force and precise orbital strikes; its arsenal consists of aggressive laser weapons and excellent fire control systems.
LoadBrief:Pacific: Pacific Island Chain (PIC) combines cryo and nano technologies for frontal power, emphasizing long-range firepower and amphibious warfare, providing strong battlefield support.
LoadBrief:YuriMind: Mind Mandate (EPM) possesses terrifying supernatural technology, using psychic powers and gravity fields to control the battlefield; its hero can even capture buildings.
LoadBrief:YuriGen: Chaos Legion (ECL) specializes in gene editing, mutating enemy infantry to disrupt battlefields or enhancing their own infantry for superior individual power.
LoadBrief:YuriVirus: Ares Order (EAO) focuses on biochemical weapons, using specialized bio-weapons to cause chaos; mass poison gas is the nightmare of infantry.
