renwu:sov00910: Qianzhi: "I'm sure you've noticed, how could Soviet Russia have such a complete base? There may be more to it."
renwu:sov0096: Qianzhi: "Anyway, in this mission, another of our generals will lead the main force to attack; what you need to do is build a solid military base."
