renwu:sov00911: Qianzhi: "Here are some missile carriers captured from the enemy; they can tear through enemy heavy armor and fortifications from a distance. Make good use of them."
renwu:sov00924: Qianzhi: "Hmm... but they seem damaged. Try to repair them with Engineers."
renwu:sov00925: Hint: Order Engineers to enter the Hongjian Missile Carriers.
renwu:sov00926: Tianyu: "Damn, this tank's armor is too thick. I can't snipe its driver. Maybe missiles would work?"
renwu:sov00927: Hint: Tianyu's sniper rifle cannot kill the driver of Apocalypse Tanks. You need other units to deal with it.
