Description:TipsRussians: Tips: Soviet Russia is centered around EMP; using EMP can easily turn the tide of battle!
Description:TipsConfederation: Tips: Atlas Confederation excels at guerrilla warfare; harass early or you'll suffer later!
Description:TipsChina: Tips: Don't let Eastern United Front reach late game, or you'll eat ICBMs QAQ
Description:TipsAmericans: Tips: Don't underestimate US laser weapons and air force; they handle both armored hordes and guerrilla units with ease.
Description:TipsBritish: Tips: The Maginot Line is not a joke; try attacking Europa Joint Council's defenses and see.
Description:TipsAlliance: Tips: If you want an arctic trip, try Pacific Island Chain's cryo tech first~
Description:TipsYuriMind: Tips: When you see a tank with a brain, remember one word: "RUN"!
Description:TipsYuriGen: Tips: Erebus "fitness" technology, you can trust!
Description:TipsYuriVirus: Tips: No matter how many infantry attack Ares Order, they'll just leave behind poison clouds.
THEME:SrLiYueRemix: Xianzhou & Liyue Battle Theme Remix
renwu:all00911: Allied Intel Officer: "MCV and supplies have arrived. Now under your command. Our satellites have locked this area, so we've regained satellite map."
Description:Tip9: "An iron curtain has descended across the continent of Europe." — Winston Churchill
Description:Tip10: "Strategy is the brain, tactics are the limbs; both are indispensable." — Military Proverb
Description:Tip11: "Technology is the primary combat power, innovation is the eternal theme." — Military Maxim
Description:Tip12: "Steel tide crushes obstacles, precision strikes hit vital points." — Military Maxim
Description:Tip13: "War is the continuation of politics; the art of war lies in the hearts of men." — Military Proverb
Description:Tip14: "All warfare is based on deception; surprise wins." — Sun Tzu's Art of War
Description:Tip15: "The human brain is a Pandora's box full of charges; we are only beginning to understand it." — Yuri
Description:Tip16: "In battle, use the orthodox to engage, and the unorthodox to win." — Sun Tzu's Art of War, Shih Pian
Description:Tip17: "The supreme art of war is to subdue the enemy without fighting." — Sun Tzu's Art of War, Mou Gong Pian
Description:Tip18: "There are no constant tactics, just as there is no constant form; he who can adapt and win is divine." — Sun Tzu's Art of War, Xu Shi Pian
Description:Tip19: "Victory and strength bring submission." — Sun Bin's Art of War, Jian Wei Wang
Description:Tip20: "Momentum is what makes soldiers fight." — Sun Bin's Art of War, Shi Bei
Description:Tip21: "Divide and conquer, then concentrate and strike." — Sun Bin's Art of War, Wei Wang Wen
Description:Tip22: "The four essentials of military: formation, momentum, variation, and authority." — Sun Bin's Art of War, Shi Bei
Description:Tip23: "Know yourself and know your enemy, and you will never be defeated." — Sun Tzu's Art of War, Mou Gong Pian
Description:Tip24: "War is deception." — Sun Tzu's Art of War, Ji Pian
Description:Tip25: "Speed is essential in war; delay is costly." — Sun Tzu's Art of War, Zuo Zhan Pian
Description:Tip26: "Without favorable timing, terrain, and unity, victory brings disaster." — Sun Bin's Art of War, Yue Zhan
Description:Tip27: "Avoid the strong and attack the weak." — Sun Tzu's Art of War, Xu Shi Pian
Description:Tip28: Did you know? Command & Conquer: War of Dawn was first publicly released on June 12, 2022~
Description:Tip29: "If soldiers come, we block; if water comes, we dam." — from the play "Da Battle of Pitong"
