Description:WEIXING: Reveals terrain under shroud via satellite
Description:ForceShield: Protects buildings in small area from all damage
  But causes base blackout for a period
Description:SpyPlaneSpecial: Calls a reconnaissance aircraft at target location
  Aircraft reveals shroud it passes over
Description:ForceShieldUnit: Provides an energy shield to units (not buildings) in an area
  Shield counts as heavy armor and absorbs 200 damage
Description:PsyReveal: Reveals terrain under shroud
Description:Chrono: Designate 3x3 area and target location
  Chrono-teleports units to that location
  Teleporting infantry kills them (except Chrono Legionnaire)
  Cannot teleport buildings
Description:Storm: Controls weather in an area
  Shrouds target area with thunderclouds
  Clouds periodically strike lightning
Description:Iron: Makes vehicles in 3x3 area invulnerable
  Lasts for a period
  Cannot be used on infantry and kills infantry
Description:NukeSpecial: Weakened atomic bomb
  Deals devastating damage to target area
  Alarm sounds at target
  [Psychic Detector] can predict its impact point
Description:D14SP: Eastern United Front's ultimate weapon
