Name:LRFSV: Xiyue Fire Support Vehicle
Description:LRFSV: 【Side】Soviet Union - Eastern United Front
  【Unit Type】T3 Anti-armor Unit
  【Armor】Heavy Armor
  【Weapons】 
    [Xiyue Missile]
    -Damage Type: AP
    -Anti-armor
    -Upon hit, deploys a [Mini Terror Drone] at target (which self-destructs actively)
    -Alternates with [EMP Missile]
    -Only in Form 1
    [EMP Missile]
    -Damage Type: HE
    -Anti-armor, anti-building
    -Reduces enemy movement and attack speed by 40%
    -Only in Form 1
    [Electronic Countermeasure System]
    -Deploys full spectrum ECM, losing mobility
    -Reduces movement and attack speed of all armored units in area by 60% (friend and foe)
    -Gives friendly units in area 15% chance to dodge damage (non-stackable)
    -Only in Form 2
  【Special Attributes】
  -Immune to all crushing
  -Auto-repairs
  -Can be permanently upgraded by support superweapon [Xiyue: Electronic Module Upgrade]
  -Limited to 9 (shared between upgraded and non-upgraded)
  -Can enter Tank Bunkers
  -Immune to gravity effects
  -Deploy to switch between Form 1 and Form 2
