RENWU:wdsov02easy: Location: Kyiv - Dnieper River bank
  Difficulty: Easy
RENWU:wdsov02medium: Location: Kyiv - Dnieper River bank
  Difficulty: Normal
RENWU:wdsov02difficult: Location: Kyiv - Dnieper River bank
  Difficulty: Hard
RENWU:wdsov02s1: Sofia: "Comrade General, our temporary defenses are complete."
RENWU:wdsov02s2: Sofia: "This is our first line of defense."
RENWU:wdsov02s3: Sofia: "The first line is commanded by Colonel Mikhail, tasked with stopping the first Allied wave."
RENWU:wdsov02s4: Sofia: "But judging by Europa's momentum, one line won't last long."
RENWU:wdsov02s5: Sofia: "So you need to defend the second and third lines. The local forces in Kyiv are limited; the nearest Ural Group is rushing here."
RENWU:wdsov02s5: Sofia: "Before they arrive, please make full use of local military facilities to hold off Europa."
RENWU:wdsov02s6: Sofia: "Southeast, across the Dnieper, is Kyiv. Stop the enemy from crossing!"
RENWU:wdsov02s7: Sofia: "If Kyiv falls, Stalingrad will be wide open and defenseless. Stalingrad is our vital supply and transport hub."
RENWU:wdsov02s8: Sofia: "If we hold them, we'll have time to fortify Kyiv, Leningrad, Stalingrad, and Moscow."
RENWU:wdsov02s9: Sofia: "Wait... it seems the first Allied wave is starting."
RENWU:wdsov02s10: Sofia: "According to intel, the Allies have retrofitted old equipment; performance and armor have greatly improved."
RENWU:wdsov02s11: Sofia: "Just their vanguard is already breaking our first line."
RENWU:wdsov02s12: Sofia: "They're assembling a second wave; we must reinforce quickly!"
RENWU:wdsov02s13: Sofia: "You failed to hold the line; the Allies will occupy Kyiv soon."
RENWU:wdsov02s14: Sofia: "Make good use of Tunnel Entrances; our soldiers can quickly transfer between positions."
RENWU:wdsov02stime: Time until Ural Group arrives:
Name:WDSOV02: Mission: Defense of Kyiv - Location: Ukraine - Kyiv - Dnieper River bank
LoadMsg:WDSOV02: Mission: Defense of Kyiv - Location: Ukraine - Kyiv - Dnieper River bank
LoadBrief:WDSOV02: >Objective 1: Hold out until Ural Group arrives.
  >Objective 2: Destroy Europa Joint Council's forward base.
Brief:WDSOV02: The Allies have officially declared war; Europa Joint Council launched the first attack on the western front.
  They are clearly prepared; we had to hastily set up a temporary defense. Losing Kyiv would be disastrous for the battle situation. We must hold it!
